<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    @font-face {
        font-family: "Siemreap";
        src: url({#asset KhmerOSSiemreapRegular.ttf  @encoding=dataURI});
        format('ttf');
    }
    @font-face {
        font-family: "KhmerOSMuol";
        src: url({#asset KhmerOSMuolLightRegular.ttf  @encoding=dataURI});
        format('ttf');
    }

    @font-face {
      font-family: "Roman";
      src: url({#asset times new roman.ttf  @encoding=dataURI});
      format('ttf');
    }
    body {
        font-size: 15px;
        font-family: "Roman", "Siemreap";
    }
    .indent-paragraph{
        text-indent: 68px;
    }
    /* FONT */
    .font_muol {
        font-family: "Roman", "KhmerOSMuol";
    }
    .font_siemreap {
        font-family: "Roman", "Siemreap";
    }
    .font_tacteing {
        font-family: "Tacteing";
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html,
    body {
      margin: 0px;
      padding: 0px;
    }

    .main {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
    }

    .header {
      width: 100%;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid black;
    }
  </style>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>

<body>
  {{#each $pdf.pages}}
  {{#if @index}}
  <div style="page-break-before: always;"></div>
  {{/if}}
    <main class="main">
        <header></header>
        <footer class="w-full border-t border-black pb-6 text-[12px] pt-2">
            <div class="w-full flex justify-between">
                <p class="text-start">
                    អាសយដ្ឋាន៖ ភូមិបាក់ខែង សង្កាត់បាក់ខែង ខណ្ឌជ្រោយចង្វារ​ រាជធានីភ្នំពេញ
                </p>
                <p class="float-right">{{getPageNumber @index "km"}}/{{getTotalPages ../$pdf.pages}}</p>
            </div>
        </footer>
    </main>
  {{/each}}
</body>

</html>